BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 170.09 Td (The user-facing workflow is documented by the project and can be summarized as follows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 151.29 Td (For predefined sections, the user selects a section type, enters the required dimensions, applies) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 137.49 Td (the calculation, and reviews the property table. H, box, pipe, and crane girder parameter names) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 123.69 Td (match the API definitions. Invalid or physically impossible combinations produce diagnostics; users) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 109.89 Td (are expected to correct input values and recalculate.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 91.09 Td (For stress output points, the user reviews the generated points, edits global coordinates if) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 77.29 Td (needed, and observes updated principal coordinates. Stress points are output locations for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 48.00 63.49 Td (reporting; they are not required to coincide with mesh nodes.) Tj ET
